<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182081>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1¯3. Eutichurus paredesi new species. Male: 1 palp, ventral view; 2 embolus, prolateral view; 3 palp, retrolateral view.Abbreviations: aMA—apices of MA; apMA—apices of median prong of MA; MA—median apophysis.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182081/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182083>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4¯8. Eutichurus murgai new species. Male: 4 palp, ventral view; 5 embolus, prolateral view; 6 palp, retrolateral view. Female: 7 epigynum, ventral view; 8 epigynum, dorsal view. Abbreviations: aMA—apices of MA; AP—anterior projection of lateral lobe; apMA—apices of median prong of MA; CD—copulatory duct; MF—median field; PP—posterior plate of lateral lobe; S1—primary spermathecae; S2—secondary spermathecae; SS2—stalk of S2.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182083/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182085>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9¯11. Eutichurus zarate Bonaldo, 1994. Male: 9 palp, ventral view; 10 embolus, prolateral view; 11 palp, retrolateral view.Abbreviations:C—conductor; MA—median apophysis. Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182087>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12¯14. Eutichurus cumbia new species. Male: 12 palp, ventral view; 13 embolus, prolateral view; 14 palp, retrolateral view Abbreviations:aMA—apices of MA; C—conductor; MA—median apophysis.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182087/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182089>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15¯19. Eutichurus yungas new species. Male. 15 palp, ventral view; 16 embolus, prolateral view; 17 palp, retrolateral view.Female. 18 epigynum, ventral view; 19 epigynum, dorsal view.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182091>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20¯22. Eutichurus tequendama new species. Male: 20 palp, ventral view; 21 embolus, prolateral view; 22 palp, retrolateral view.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182095>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27¯29. Eutichurus marquesae Bonaldo, 1994. Male: 27 palp, ventral view; 28 embolus, prolateral view; 29 palp, retrolateral view.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182107>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58¯65. Eutichurus nancyae new species. Male: 58 palp, ventral view (arrow: ventral lamellae); 59 embolus, prolateral view; 60 palp, retrolateral view. Female: 61 epigynum, ventral view; 62 epigynum, dorsal view. Eutichurus ibiuna Bonaldo, 1994. Female: 63 epigynum, ventral view; 64 epigynum, dorsal view; 65 epigynum, posterior view. Abbreviations: AP—anterior projection of lateral lobe; MF—median field; PP—posteriorplate of lateral lobe.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182093>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23¯26. Eutichurus madre Bonaldo, 1994. Male: 23 palp, ventral view; 24 embolus, prolateral view; 25 palp, retrolateral view.Female:26 epigynum, dorsal view.Scale bar = 0,25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1182105>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52¯57. Eutichurus marquesae Bonaldo, 1994. Female: epigynum, 52 ventral view; 53 posterior view; 54 dorsal view; 55 dorso-lateral view; 56 dorso-anterior view; 57 cuticular glands. Abbreviatures: AP—anterior projection of lateral lobe; CD—copulatory duct; CG—cuticular gland; FD—fertilization duct; MF—median field; PP—posterior plate of lateral lobe; S1—primary spermathecae; S2—secondary spermathecae; SS2—stalk of S2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1182105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

